8 POLICY COMMITTEE RECOMMENDATION
9 An Act relating to retirement; amending 47 O.S. 2021,
Section 2-300, as last amended by Section 1, Chapter
10 361, O.S.L. 2024 (47 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 2-300),
which relates to the Oklahoma Law Enforcement
11 Retirement System; defining term; providing for
participation of certain new employees in the
12 Oklahoma Law Enforcement Retirement System; providing
for codification; and declaring an emergency.
13
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 47 O.S. 2021, Section 2-300, as
18 last amended by Section 1, Chapter 361, O.S.L. 2024 (47 O.S. Supp.
